---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from "../consts";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>Meet <em>Lucas Silva</em> 🎉</h1>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Age:</strong> 27 years old 🎂</li>
        <li>
          <strong>Location:</strong> The enchanting city of <em>Porto</em> 🏰
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        He's not just your average guy - no, <em>Lucas</em> is a whirlwind of quirky
        passions and unbridled enthusiasm for all things weird and wonderful 🚀.
      </p>
      <p>
        When he's not lost in the world of <strong>bleeding-edge tech</strong> 💻
        or conquering virtual metropolises in city-building games, you'll find <em
          >Lucas</em
        > meticulously crafting the ultimate gaming rig or engaging in heated debates
        over the merits of different types of screws for hanging paintings 🔩. Yes,
        he's that <strong>dedicated</strong> 💪.
      </p>
      <p>
        But <em>Lucas</em>'s adventures don't stop there. In his cozy townhouse,
        he reigns supreme alongside his <strong>feline overlord</strong> 🐱 and partner-in-crime,
        all while savoring the delights of his favorite food: <em>sushi</em> 🍣.
        Because nothing says "<em>living life to the fullest</em>" like
        indulging in raw fish delicacies 🎣.
      </p>
      <p>
        And let's not forget <em>Lucas</em>'s legendary <strong
          >stubbornness</strong
        > 💢 - a trait matched only by his <strong>insatiable curiosity</strong>
        🤔. Whether it's arguing over the optimal strategy for a city-wide traffic
        system or delving into the mysteries of <strong>AI</strong> 🤖, <em
          >Lucas</em
        > approaches every challenge with gusto and a healthy dose of <strong
          >humor</strong
        > 😄.
      </p>
      <p>
        So, here's to <em>Lucas Silva</em> - the <strong>tech-savvy</strong> 💻,
        <em>sushi-loving</em> 🍣, <em>screw-obsessed</em> 🔩 maestro of eccentricity.
        May his adventures continue to entertain and inspire us all 🎭.
      </p>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
